# College Management System Logic Update

Complete restructure of admissions, registration, sessions, documents, and login logic.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Breaking changes to student login:** Roll Number becomes the default username. Existing students whose username ≠ rollNumber will still work because auth.ts matches by username OR email OR rollNumber. New students will have `username = rollNumber`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Batch removal:** The [Batch](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28admin%29/admin/students/page.tsx#14-15) model and [Class](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Class.ts#3-10) model are NOT deleted (other parts of the system — attendance, exams, assignments — still reference them). Instead, we stop exposing batch selection in the student registration flow. The student is directly assigned to a **Program** (course). The admin can still manage batches internally for attendance/scheduling.

> [!WARNING]
> **Document schema change:** [StudentDocuments](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentDocuments.ts#10-28) model gets new fields (`aadhaarFrontUrl`, `aadhaarBackUrl`, `documentMeta`). Existing Aadhaar data stored in `aadhaarIdUrl` will remain accessible. A migration is not needed — old records just won't have the new fields populated.

