## 1. Intake & Joining Logic

### [NEW] [CollegeSettings.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CollegeSettings.ts)
- New model to store configurable settings:
  - `academicSession` (string, e.g. `"2024-25"`)
  - `intakeMonths` (array, default `["January", "July"]`)
  - Singleton pattern — only one document, fetched via `CollegeSettings.getSingleton()`

### [MODIFY] [User.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/User.ts)
- **Add**: `joiningMonth` (enum: `'January' | 'July'`), `joiningYear` (Number)
- **Add**: `courseEndDate` (Date) — auto-calculated
- **Remove from required**: `sessionFrom`, `sessionTo` (keep in schema for legacy, make optional)

### [MODIFY] [register route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts)
- Replace `sessionFrom`/`sessionTo` inputs with `joiningMonth` + `joiningYear`
- Auto-calculate `courseEndDate = joiningMonth/joiningYear + Program.duration_years`
- Batch is looked up from Program + active session, NOT selected by student
- Username = rollNumber

### [MODIFY] [complete-profile page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/complete-profile/page.tsx)
- Replace "Session From / Session To" dropdowns with:
  - **Joining Month**: dropdown with only "January" / "July"
  - **Joining Year**: dropdown (years list)
- Auto-show calculated course end date
- Remove batch dropdown — student selects **Program** (course) instead
- Show auto-calculated "Course End: Month Year"

### [MODIFY] [complete-profile route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/complete-profile/route.ts)
- Same logic: accept `joiningMonth`, `joiningYear`, `programId` instead of `batchId`, `sessionFrom`, `sessionTo`
- Auto-calculate course end date from `Program.duration_years`

