## 4. Document Upload & Verification

### [MODIFY] [StudentDocuments.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentDocuments.ts)
- **Add**: `aadhaarFrontUrl`, `aadhaarFrontType`, `aadhaarBackUrl`, `aadhaarBackType` (all required)
- **Add**: `documentMeta` array — `{ docType, docNumber, docRollNumber?, docPercentage? }`
  - Ex: `{ docType: '10th', docRollNumber: '12345', docPercentage: '85.2' }`
  - Ex: `{ docType: 'Aadhaar', docNumber: '1234-5678-9012' }`
- Make aadhaar fields required (both front + back)

### [MODIFY] [complete-profile page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/complete-profile/page.tsx)
- Move Aadhaar from OPTIONAL_DOCS → REQUIRED_DOCS (split into front + back)
- Add metadata form fields per document:
  - **10th**: Roll Number + Percentage
  - **12th**: Roll Number + Percentage
  - **Aadhaar**: Aadhaar Number (12 digits)
  - **Other**: Relevant ID Number
- Validate mandatory fields before submission

### [MODIFY] [complete-profile route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/complete-profile/route.ts)
- Accept `aadhaarFront` and `aadhaarBack` files (both mandatory)
- Accept `docMeta` JSON field with document metadata
- Validate Aadhaar number format, 10th/12th roll + percentage
- Save to `StudentDocuments.documentMeta`

### [MODIFY] [student/profile page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(student)/student/profile/page.tsx)
- Show Aadhaar Front + Back separately
- Display document metadata (roll numbers, aadhaar number, percentages)

### [MODIFY] [admin/students page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(admin)/admin/students/page.tsx)
